      <description>&lt;p&gt;講起《死亡擱淺》（Death Stranding），不少玩家當年都説是「送貨或行山模擬器」，甚至有些玩家接受不到那種遊戲節奏及玩法，玩不久就棄 Game。不過小島秀夫這款作品，偏偏就有人愈玩愈沉迷，愈玩愈上癮。今次續作《死亡擱淺 2：冥灘之上》，承繼前作獨有玩法，再大幅強化系統、畫面、節奏，令整體體驗大提升。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624102013_" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610421111/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610421111_22c06d139b_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624102013_" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="365" data-end="385"&gt;送貨玩法依舊不過爽好多&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="387" data-end="477"&gt;今集劇情設定在前作完結後 11 個月，Sam 與 BB Lou(路) 過著退休隱居生活，直到 Fragile 找他返來幫手，加入新成立的「Drawbridge」，再一次踏上送貨救世界的路途。玩法上，依然係經典的「取貨 — 行路 — 交貨 」，但系統優化做得很出色：路線規劃，裝備整理及平衡控制都順手很多；一開波已經可以解鎖大量裝備，如外骨骼、載具，起步不再像上代那樣辛苦又緩慢，新手期更已有敵人需要打的了。而任務的節奏亦增快了，所需時間更少，劇情與探索穿插自然，不再像之前組常對著 hologram 角色講十幾分鐘對白既悶場面。送貨路途愈長時，反而會愈期待下個新故事的推進及發展。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="387" data-end="477"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250623192735" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610421336/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610421336_01411f7a72_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250623192735" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624001500" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610421246/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610421246_08cc449d1f_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624001500" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="387" data-end="477"&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_02.31.010" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610632858/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610632858_bf4a1bb1e8_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_02.31.010" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="387" data-end="477"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624111015" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610421071/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610421071_2abc4abe86_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624111015" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="661" data-end="687"&gt;送貨之路隨時變災難片&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="689" data-end="817"&gt;《死亡擱淺 2》最大亮點之一，就是環境系統進化得誇張。暴雨會令河流水位飆升、泥石流隨時可以沖走你剛剛建好的橋，沙塵暴遮擋著視野、強風吹得你左搖右擺，再加上時間雨腐蝕貨物，隨時前功盡廢。你搭建的設施會隨時間損壞，不定時去維修或重建，送貨不再是例行公事，隨時會遇敵人及 BT 變成生死戰；環境系統亦變成真正「活著」的敵人，迫你每次都要因應現場情況即時部署，不再會有兩次旅程是完全一樣，可以説每次起行都會是一場新冒險。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="689" data-end="817"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624000921" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610622769/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610622769_b07874b223_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624000921" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="689" data-end="817"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624101442" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610633233/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610633233_a90f637baf_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624101442" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="889" data-end="909"&gt;戰鬥進化：潛行或硬拼任你揀&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="911" data-end="1010"&gt;上一集戰鬥體驗偏生硬，又少變化，今集完全是大改進及強化，令小編估不到的是開波的送貨路線已經可以開打了。而潛行系統加入更多誘敵道具、感應裝置、匿蹤技巧，敵人 AI 又聰明，會隨時吹雞叫人支援，用電擊武器、甚至會飛天追擊。當然你不想硬碰戰鬥都得，送貨任務你可以選取避戰路線，專心送貨；不過有些任務是強制要你打大怪的，例如打大型 BT，你不得戰鬥不行，所以還是操如練一下為妙。而新武器及道具選擇都超多，手槍、裝機槍，進化子彈又可直接打 BT；手榴彈又分血液及液體等等，每樣效果都不同；用電棍打近戰又得。戰鬥遠比一代好玩，更多樣化，亦耐玩得多。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="911" data-end="1010"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624104707" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610633168/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610633168_947ba0922c_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624104707" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624153928" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610622609/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610622609_8f4a8bff9e_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624153928" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_30.04.922" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610622274/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610622274_8a135869a9_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_30.04.922" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="1096" data-end="1119"&gt;全球玩家一齊砌條更好行的路&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1121" data-end="1226"&gt;Chyro Network 連接擴展亦可説是今代重心，隨著你解鎖新區域，可以搭建道路、橋樑、滑索、充電站、農場，令整個交通網絡愈砌愈齊。你所建造的設施會被全球其他玩家共享，見到自己搭的索道有人用，充電站有人俾 Like (可見到玩家俾 Like 數字)，真的更有成就感，愈玩愈感受到「人與人連結」的遊戲哲學。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1121" data-end="1226"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624095446" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54609546092/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54609546092_43730dc1c6_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624095446" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624111145" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54609546007/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54609546007_0c540071f4_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624111145" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="1291" data-end="1309"&gt;畫面及聲音表現滿分&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1625" data-end="1739"&gt;《死亡擱淺 2》再次展現小島製作的視覺執著。雨中泥濘、濕潤巖壁、紅霧瀰漫的 BT 區域，每一個場景細節都達到近乎寫實的視覺表現；角色面部表情、裝備細節、粒子特效全方位升級，尤其是 Sam 那張歷盡風霜的臉，幾乎可見毛孔與歲月痕跡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1625" data-end="1739"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624162348" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54609545892/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54609545892_d0baabe182_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624162348" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.19.538" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610420901/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610420901_c5726eb93c_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.19.538" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.43.806" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610727685/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610727685_ff0c6f3ae2_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.43.806" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1741" data-end="1893"&gt;聲音表現更是神來之筆，風雨聲、腳步陷入泥濘的吱吱聲、緊張時刻心跳聲全都層層堆疊，營造出既孤獨又危險的探索氣氛。當 BT 接近時，環境聲逐漸抽離，只餘探測器咔咔作響與急促喘息，令人全程神經繃緊。配樂方面，依舊大量運用歌曲，許多重要任務與劇情轉折點會有不同的原創歌曲進場，情感渲染極強，令人難忘。壯麗的場景再加上出色的音樂配搭，小編就非常享受送貨旅程了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1741" data-end="1893"&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.57.939" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610632963/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610632963_2499a8243c_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_00.57.939" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start="1900" data-end="1921"&gt;奇異、深刻、耐玩的獨特體驗&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1923" data-end="2071"&gt;如果你曾經喜歡《死亡擱淺》那份孤獨、慢熱、哲學式的送貨冒險，《死亡擱淺 2》可説是夢想中的進化版，節奏大幅改善，系統全面優化，玩法層次更為豐富。但如果你當年完全無法接受那種「慢慢行、慢慢搬貨」玩法，今次其實本質並未大變，依然是那款送貨模擬器玩法，所不同的是，節奏不再是那麼的慢，加入更多戰鬥元素；而小編對今集就甚為喜愛了，甚至是多日也玩不停手。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="1923" data-end="2071"&gt;&lt;a title="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624142940" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610622614/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610622614_a9d79036bd_b.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20250624142940" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="2073" data-end="2190"&gt;《死亡擱淺 2》完美演繹了小島式遊戲哲學，將「連結」與「孤獨」並存，把一個看似單純的送貨系統，變成充滿戰略、挑戰與人性反思的冒險歷程。它可能也未必是「大眾向」的遊戲，但對願意投入其中的玩家，這絕對是一場不可多得的奇幻旅程。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start="2073" data-end="2190"&gt;&lt;a title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_18.08.137" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202676835@N04/54610420621/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54610420621_01937f939d_b.jpg" alt="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - PS5 PS5 Pro - Digital Foundry Tech Review - 4K HDR.mp4_snapshot_18.08.137" width="1024" height="576" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/06/24/death-stranding-2-on-the-beach-review/game-channel/game-review/"&gt;【評測】《死亡擱淺，冥灘之上 Death Stranding 2 On The Beach》    系統進化送貨更過癮&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a href="https://unwire.hk"&gt;UNWIRE.HK&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
