      <title>金管局監管「穩定幣」，8 月接受牌照申請，初期僅批數個牌照門檻甚高</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/06/24/hk-stablecoin-regulation/life-tech/crypto-blockchain/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=hk-stablecoin-regulation</link>
